dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.resource.spec.ResourceSpecVersionDetails
dataStructure.description:
This class defines the semantics of the modifiesResourceSpec aggregation. Specifically, it enables an application to define which set of versions of this ResourceSpecification are appropriate for a given task.This aggregation represents the set of versions of this ResourceSpecification. The semantics of this aggregation are implemented with the ResourceSpecVersionDetails class.

This association class is optional
dataStructure.label: ResourceSpecVersionDetails

child.name: resourceSpecVerValidFor
child.description:
This attribute defines a time period which this particular ResourceSpecVersion is applicable. This enables past versions of a ResourceSpecification to be designated as no longer applicable.

This element is generated from an attribute.

This attribute is optional
child.label: resourceSpecVerValidFor

child.name: preferredVersionToUse
child.description:
This attribute defines the preferred Version of this ResourceSpecification to use.

This element is generated from an attribute.

This attribute is optional
child.label: preferredVersionToUse

child.name: minVersionForUse
child.description:
This attribute defines the minimal version of this ResourceSpecification to use.

This element is generated from an attribute.

This attribute is optional
child.label: minVersionForUse
